 Boundary conditions:
 -------------------

                     p                    uv                                  pt

 B. bound.: p(0)     = p(1)   | uv(0)     = 0                     | pt(0)     = from soil model  
 T. bound.: p(nzt+1) = 0      | uv(nzt+1) = ug(nzt+1), vg(nzt+1)  | pt(nzt+1) = pt(nzt) + dpt/dz_

                     e

 B. bound.: e(0)     = e(1)                                                                      
 T. bound.: e(nzt+1) = e(nzt) = e(nzt-1)                                                         

                     q

 B. bound.: q(0)     = from soil model                                                           
 T. bound.: q(nzt+1) = q(nzt) + dq/dz                                                            

